text: Nannodiella is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Clathurellidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Nannodiella include: * Nannodiella acricula (Hedley, 1922) * Nannodiella baracoesa Espinosa, Ortea & Moro, 2017 * Nannodiella candidula (Reeve, 1846) * Nannodiella cubadiella Espinosa, Ortea & Moro, 2017 * Nannodiella elatior (d'Orbigny, 1847) * Nannodiella fraternalis (Dall, 1919) * Nannodiella hukuiensis (Nomura & Niino, 1940) * Nannodiella melanitica (Dall, 1901) * Nannodiella nana (Dall, 1919) * Nannodiella oxia (Bush, 1885) * Nannodiella vespuciana (d'Orbigny, 1842) ==References== ==External links== * Dall W.H.
